- [whistle blows]

2150
01:25:13,609 --> 01:25:15,486
Let me at him! Let me at him!

2151
01:25:15,569 --> 01:25:17,112
- Relax!
- [whistle blows]

2152
01:25:17,196 --> 01:25:19,114
- [groans]
- Keep your hooves

2153
01:25:19,198 --> 01:25:20,491
off my teammates.

2154
01:25:20,574 --> 01:25:21,742
Get him, Daddy!

2155
01:25:21,826 --> 01:25:23,536
Make him bleed!

2156
01:25:23,619 --> 01:25:25,120
That's not what you want to see.

2157
01:25:25,204 --> 01:25:26,539
Speak for yourself.

2158
