- [Mane] Cry about it.

2161
01:25:33,712 --> 01:25:36,090
[Chuck] <i>The rules state</i>
<i>Thorns need five players</i>

2162
01:25:36,173 --> 01:25:37,258
- <i>or they forfeit.</i>
- Hit me again.

2163
01:25:37,341 --> 01:25:38,342
[bell dings]

2164
01:25:39,009 --> 01:25:41,011
