2174
01:25:59,405 --> 01:26:02,575
No. We can't let you do this.
You'll just make it worse.

2175
01:26:02,658 --> 01:26:03,701
You think they bought it?

2176
01:26:03,784 --> 01:26:04,827
[all gasp]

2177
01:26:04,910 --> 01:26:06,078
Um, I do.

2178
01:26:06,161 --> 01:26:09,164
